title: ASK ANDY:  Choosing Partners, Slaying Giants - MFQA2
description: How do you choose the right partner to go into business?  How can you compete in an industry that is dominated by one or two giant companies?  In his trademark no b.s. style, The MFCEO Andy Frisella answers these questions. Joining him in the studio is his co-host, Vaughn Kohler.
